\v 1 Tsa² jnco³ xi³ jin³-no³ nca³ jon² xi³ tjin¹ i⁴tse¹-le⁴ cjoa⁴ cao⁴ xi³jnco³, a³ coan⁴nˀion¹con³ nca³ coai⁴con³-le⁴ cjoa⁴-te¹xo³ma³ xi³ tsˀe⁴ je² xi³ tsi² qui²xi⁴ tjio¹ma³, cˀoa⁴ nca³ tsi² nqui³xcon⁴ cho⁴ta⁴-le⁴ Cristo.
