\v 19 A³xo⁴ tsi² tsa² ˀyao³ nca³ je² yao³-no³ ntˀia³-le⁴ Espíritu Santo ni¹, je² xi³ ti¹jna³jin³-no³ nca³ jon², jña³-le⁴ xi³ tsˀe⁴ Ni³na¹ tjin¹-ni³no³, cˀoa⁴ nca³ tsi² ti⁴tsaon⁴³-nio³ nca³ jon².
